      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p style="text-align: justify;">
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Guide 1 &#8211; Party Time / Rhythm Piano</strong><br />
Understand good<a href="http://d2c6bn6g-931euaemwsfgzmacn.hop.clickbank.net/"> <span style="color: #3366ff;">rhythm model piano</span></a> straight away with piano chords, 10 classic party rhythms, a terrific piano <a title="Chord (music)" rel="wikipedia" href="http://d2c6bn6g-931euaemwsfgzmacn.hop.clickbank.net/">chord</a> ballad, lots of keyboard diagrams, tricks, and loads of progressions while in the fashion of classic songs. Within days you&#8217;ll be the life and soul belonging to the party! (15 Movies / 101 AUDIO)</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Guide 2 &#8211; Shake.. Rattle &#8216;n&#8217; Roll..</strong><br />
Now it is possible to play some great Blues and Rock &#8216;n&#8217; Roll Piano. Instantly recognisable rhythms that is usually employed for hundreds of classic songs. Amaze your friends with the sounds of Fat&#8217;s Domino, Jerry Lee Lewis, Little Richard and also a host of others. It is effortless whenever you know how! (7 Videos / 15 AUDIO)</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Guide 3 &#8211; Chord Magic</strong><br />
Understand more piano chords applying amazing memory tricks and play some excellent practice progressions while in the style of popular songs. Master to change piano chords at speed implementing Inversions. A special piano chord chart and some speed learning exercises will assist you master your chords in next to no time! (4 Videos / 38 AUDIO)</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Guide 4 &#8211; Innovative Chords Manufactured Effortless</strong><br />
You might be now ready to master some advanced piano chords but Pianoforall helps you do it the straightforward way &#8211; not the technical way. Tons of additional practice progressions inside the style of well-known piano songs and a rhythm chart for 80 Beatles songs plus some fantastic Beatles Piano stylings. (7 Movies / 55 AUDIO)</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Guide 5 &#8211; Ballad Fashion</strong><br />
Use your knowledge of chords to build a superb <a href="http://d2c6bn6g-931euaemwsfgzmacn.hop.clickbank.net/" target="_blank"><span style="color: #3366ff;">piano ballad style</span></a> and apply it to melodies in just 3 simple steps. Study to improvise and develop your own melodies &#8211; the fun way! By the end in the guide you will probably be playing some terrific songs. This isn&#8217;t bland &#8220;easy&#8221; piano &#8211; you will sound like you&#8217;ve been playing for years! (33 Movies / 65 AUDIO)</p>
