      <description>Imagine being able to sit down at a piano and just PLAY &amp;#8211; Pop, Blues, Jazz, Ragtime, Ballads, even incredible Classical pieces? Now you can.. and you can do it in months not years! Imagine you could understand piano or keyboard without having to spend cash, time and effort on traditional Piano Lessons.
The Pianoforall [...]&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/jazz-piano-chords/Jazz_Piano_Chords-Learning_Piano_Is_Simple.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p style="text-align: justify;"><img src="file:///C:/DOCUME%7E1/ibCafe/LOCALS%7E1/Temp/moz-screenshot-2.png" alt="" /><img src="file:///C:/DOCUME%7E1/ibCafe/LOCALS%7E1/Temp/moz-screenshot-3.png" alt="" /><a href="http://d2c6bn6g-931euaemwsfgzmacn.hop.clickbank.net/" target="_blank"><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-32" style="border: 1px solid black; margin: 2px 1px;" title="piano" src="http://www.jazzpianochords.org/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/piano.jpg" alt="" width="113" height="130" /></a> Imagine being able to sit down at a piano and just PLAY &#8211; Pop, Blues, Jazz, Ragtime, Ballads, even incredible Classical pieces? Now you can.. and you can do it in months not years! Imagine you could understand piano or keyboard without having to spend cash, time and effort on traditional <a href="http://d2c6bn6g-931euaemwsfgzmacn.hop.clickbank.net/" target="_blank"><span style="color: #3366ff;">Piano Lessons.</span></a></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>The Pianoforall Method is uncomplicated..</strong></p>
<p>You start with Well-known Chord based Rhythm Style Piano (think of artists like Elton John, Billy Joel, Lennon &amp; McCartney, Barry Mannilow, Lionel Ritchie, Coldplay, Norah Jones and so on) which is EASY but sounds amazingly like the &#8216;real thing&#8217;. This enables you to achieve a professional sound almost immediately. Once you are sounding great and having a whole lot of fun (which motivates you to learn more) you then expand step-by-step on your chord and rhythm knowledge into Blues, Ballad style, Jazz, Ragtime, Improvisation and yes.. even sight reading <a href="http://d2c6bn6g-931euaemwsfgzmacn.hop.clickbank.net/" target="_blank"><span style="color: #3366ff;">classical music</span></a>.</p>
